job.title: Madras High Court Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for 3557 Office Asst, Copyist & Other Posts
job.body:
Total Vacancies:3557

Name of the post:

  • Copyist Attender/ Office Assistant, Sanitary Worker, Gardener, Watchman

Description:

Madras High Court issued a total of 3557 vacancies for the posts of Copyist Attender/ Office Assistant, Sanitary Worker, Gardener, Watchman. The online application for these posts under MHC shall start from 18-04-2021. The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before 09-07-2021. For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these posts is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The application fee for Madras High Court Recruitment 2021:

  • Mode of application: Online
  • The application fee for BC/ BCM/ MBC & DC/ Others : Rs. 500/- for each post
  • The application fee for SC/ ST: NIL
  • For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 18-04-2021
  • The Last date to apply online is 09-07-2021

Educational qualification:

  • You must have possessed class 8th to apply for the post of Copyist Attender/ Office Assistant,
  • You must have should be able to read & write Tamil to apply for the post of Sanitary Worker, Gardener, Watchman

Age limit criteria:

  • The minimum age required to apply is: 18years
  • The maximum age required to apply is: 37 years
  • For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

Pay Scale:

How to apply for Madras High Court Recruitment 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of MHC.
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of Copyist Attender/ Office Assistant, Sanitary Worker, Gardener, Watchman
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
